<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<odoo>
    <template id="globalgap_certification_application">
        <div>
            <table style="width:100%; border:0px;">
                <tr>
                    <td style="border:0px; background-color:white; width:30%;">
                    <p style="text-align:left;"><b>PL-México: </b><span t-field="doc.organization_id.plmx"/></p></td>
                    <td style="border:0px; background-color:white; width:30%;">
                    <p style="text-align:left;"><b>GGN: </b><span t-field="doc.organization_id.ggn"/></p></td>
                    <td style="border:0px; background-color:white; width:40%;">
                    <p style="text-align:left;"><b>Versión: </b><span t-field="doc.organization_id.globalgap_version"/></p></td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td colspan="2" style="border:0px; background-color:white; width:50%;">
                    <p style="text-align:left;"><b>Opción de Certificación: </b><span t-field="doc.organization_id.certification_option"/></p></td>
                    <td style="border:0px; background-color:white; width:50%;">
                    <p style="text-align:left;"><b>Tipo de Evaluación: </b><span t-field="doc.organization_id.evaluation_type"/></p></td>
                    
                </tr>
            </table>
            <h5 style="text-align:center;font-weight:Bold;">
                Addon
            </h5>
            <p>
                <t t-foreach="doc.organization_id.addons_ids" t-as="addon">
                   <span>* </span><span t-field="addon.name"/>
                   <br/>
                </t>
            </p>
            <table style="width:100%; border:0px;">
                <tr>
                    <td colspan="3" style="border:0px; background-color:white; width:100%;">
                    <p style="text-align:left;"><b>Nombre de la Entidad Legal: </b><span t-field="doc.organization_id.name"/></p></td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td colspan="2" style="border:0px; background-color:white; width:70%;">
                    <p style="text-align:left;"><b>Dirección: </b><span t-field="doc.organization_id.address"/></p></td>
                    <td style="border:0px; background-color:white; width:30%;">
                    <p style="text-align:left;"><b>CP: </b><span t-field="doc.organization_id.zip"/></p></td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td style="border:0px; background-color:white; width:40%;">
                    <p style="text-align:left;"><b>Ciudad: </b><span t-field="doc.organization_id.city_id"/></p></td>
                    <td style="border:0px; background-color:white; width:30%;">
                    <p style="text-align:left;"><b>Estado: </b><span t-field="doc.organization_id.state_id"/></p></td>
                    <td style="border:0px; background-color:white; width:30%;">
                    <p style="text-align:left;"><b>País: </b><span t-field="doc.organization_id.country_id"/></p></td>
                    
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td colspan="2" style="border:0px; background-color:white; width:70%;">
                    <p style="text-align:left;"><b>Email: </b><span t-field="doc.organization_id.email"/></p></td>
                    <td  style="border:0px; background-color:white; width:30%;">
                    <p style="text-align:left;"><b>Telefono: </b><span t-field="doc.organization_id.telephone"/></p></td>
                    
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td colspan="2" style="border:0px; background-color:white; width:50%;">
                    <p style="text-align:left;"><b>GLN: </b><span t-field="doc.organization_id.gln"/></p></td>
                    <td style="border:0px; background-color:white; width:50%;">
                    <p style="text-align:left;"><b>RFC: </b><span t-field="doc.organization_id.vat"/></p></td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td colspan="3" style="border:0px; background-color:white; width:100%;">
                    <p style="text-align:left;"><b>Nombre CB: </b><span t-field="doc.organization_id.previous_cb"/></p></td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td colspan="2" style="border:0px; background-color:white; width:50%;">
                    <p style="text-align:left;"><b>Latitud: </b><span t-field="doc.organization_id.latitude"/></p></td>
                    <td style="border:0px; background-color:white; width:50%;">
                    <p style="text-align:left;"><b>Longitud: </b><span t-field="doc.organization_id.longitude"/></p></td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td colspan="2" style="border:0px; background-color:white; width:70%;">
                    <p style="text-align:left;"><b>Persona de contacto: </b><span t-field="doc.organization_id.contact_name"/></p></td>
                    <td style="border:0px; background-color:white; width:50%;">
                    <p style="text-align:left;"><b>Cargo: </b><span t-field="doc.organization_id.contact_position"/></p></td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td colspan="2" style="border:0px; background-color:white; width:70%;">
                    <p style="text-align:left;"><b>Email: </b><span t-field="doc.organization_id.contact_email"/></p></td>
                    <td style="border:0px; background-color:white; width:30%;">
                    <p style="text-align:left;"><b>Telefono: </b><span t-field="doc.organization_id.contact_telephone"/></p></td>
                    </tr>
            </table>
            
            <p>
                De acuerdo a los requisitos del documento de las Reglas de Acceso a Datos, 
                (que se adjunta y se localiza en www.globalgap.org/es/documents) indicar si:
                <b><span t-field="doc.organization_id.rights_of_access"/></b>
            </p>

            <h5 style="text-align:center;font-weight:Bold;">
                INFORMACIÓN DE LOS SITIOS DE PRODUCCIÓN Y PHU
            </h5>
            <t t-foreach="doc.organization_id.production_site_ids" t-as="site">
                <p>
                    <table style="width:100%; border:0px;">
                        <tr>
                        <td colspan="2" style="border:0px; background-color:white; width:70%;">
                            <p style="text-align:left;"><b>Nombre: </b><span t-field="site.name"/></p></td>
                            <td  style="border:0px; background-color:white; width:30%;">
                            <p style="text-align:left;"><b>Tipo: </b><span t-field="site.type"/></p></td>
                            
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                            <td colspan="2" style="border:0px; background-color:white; width:70%;">
                            <p style="text-align:left;"><b>Dirección: </b><span t-field="site.address"/></p></td>
                            <td style="border:0px; background-color:white; width:30%;">
                            <p style="text-align:left;"><b>CP: </b><span t-field="site.zip"/></p></td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                            <td style="border:0px; background-color:white; width:40%;">
                            <p style="text-align:left;"><b>Ciudad: </b><span t-field="site.city_id"/></p></td>
                            <td style="border:0px; background-color:white; width:30%;">
                            <p style="text-align:left;"><b>Estado: </b><span t-field="site.state_id"/></p></td>
                            <td style="border:0px; background-color:white; width:30%;">
                            <p style="text-align:left;"><b>País: </b><span t-field="site.country_id"/></p></td>
                            
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                            <td colspan="2" style="border:0px; background-color:white; width:70%;">
                            <p style="text-align:left;"><b>Email: </b><span t-field="site.email"/></p></td>
                            <td  style="border:0px; background-color:white; width:30%;">
                            <p style="text-align:left;"><b>Telefono: </b><span t-field="site.telephone"/></p></td>
                            
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                            <td colspan="2" style="border:0px; background-color:white; width:50%;">
                            <p style="text-align:left;"><b>Latitud: </b><span t-field="site.latitude"/></p></td>
                            <td style="border:0px; background-color:white; width:50%;">
                            <p style="text-align:left;"><b>Longitud: </b><span t-field="site.longitude"/></p></td>
                        </tr>
                    </table>
                    <h6 style="text-align:center;font-weight:Bold;">
                        Información de Contacto de <b><span t-field="site.name"/></b>
                    </h6>
                    <table style="width:100%; border:0px;">
                        <tr>
                            <td colspan="3" style="border:0px; background-color:white; width:100%;">
                            <p style="text-align:left;"><b>Persona de contacto: </b><span t-field="site.contact_name"/></p></td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                            <td colspan="2" style="border:0px; background-color:white; width:70%;">
                            <p style="text-align:left;"><b>Dirección: </b><span t-field="site.contact_address"/></p></td>
                            <td style="border:0px; background-color:white; width:30%;">
                            <p style="text-align:left;"><b>CP: </b><span t-field="site.contact_zip"/></p></td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                            <td style="border:0px; background-color:white; width:40%;">
                            <p style="text-align:left;"><b>Ciudad: </b><span t-field="site.contact_city_id"/></p></td>
                            <td style="border:0px; background-color:white; width:30%;">
                            <p style="text-align:left;"><b>Estado: </b><span t-field="site.contact_state_id"/></p></td>
                            <td style="border:0px; background-color:white; width:30%;">
                            <p style="text-align:left;"><b>País: </b><span t-field="site.contact_country_id"/></p></td>
                            
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                            <td colspan="2" style="border:0px; background-color:white; width:70%;">
                            <p style="text-align:left;"><b>Email: </b><span t-field="site.contact_email"/></p></td>
                            <td style="border:0px; background-color:white; width:30%;">
                            <p style="text-align:left;"><b>Telefono: </b><span t-field="site.contact_telephone"/></p></td>
                            </tr>
                    </table>
                    <hr class="mt-0 mb-1" style="border-top: 1px solid"/>
                </p>
            </t>


        </div>
    </template>

</odoo>